                        Ausstellers,</rs> 2. <rs type="person" ref="pe__hagen_von_spielberg_QGW_II_I_118"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Hagen von Spilberch, zu den
                        zeiten <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">judenrichter</roleName> ze
                        Wienne,</rs> 3. <rs type="person" ref="pe__weichart_bei_den_minderbruedern_QGW_II_I_118"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Weichartes bei den Minnern
                        prüdern,</rs> 4. <rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_von_eslarn_FRA_II_1327_IV_23"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Nichlas von Eslarn</rs>, 5. <rs type="person" ref="pe__georg_am_kienmarkt_QGW_II_II_3245"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Jörgen an dem Chienmarchte,</rs> 6. <rs type="person" ref="pe__hermann_von_st_poelten_QGW_II_I_118"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName>
                        Hermans, <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__rudolfine_QGW_II_I_417"><add>eninchel</add></roleName><rs type="person" ref="pe__rudolfine_QGW_II_I_417">der Rudolffine eninchel von Sant
